node.text:
Bench hitter gonna burn your legs, save workout, try it and let me know if you felt it. Try 4-6 sets, 60 second every exercises, so 3 minute in row, one minute rest between sets. You can do it anywhere with some bench and its gonna kick your metabolism to burn some nice calories and flow the blood. 
 
Don't forgot take Blaster Master preworkout from @bangenergy before workout.
 
Check @bangenergy and inventor @bangenergy.CEO - Check out this! #BangEnergy #EnergyDrink #lifestyle
